headline: COR Q2 Deep Dive: Specialty Growth, International Headwinds, and Guidance Update
summary: Healthcare distributor Cencora (NYSE:COR) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 8.7% year on year to $80.66 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $4 per share was 4.2% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
